        public java.util.List<AcousticModel> getCustomizations()
        Gets the customizations. An array of objects that provides information about each available custom acoustic model. The array is empty if the requesting service credentials own no custom acoustic models (if no language is specified) or own no custom acoustic models for the specified language.
        Returns:
        the customizations
